Using the pSI R package function specificity.index (19,20), the RPKM values for each transcript were used to calculate a pSI value for that transcript in each of the tissues. pSI values were calculated for all detectably expressed (>0.3 RPKM, as per (21)) protein coding transcripts. Briefly, the pSI is calculated as follows. First, a specificity index value SI is calculated for gene i in tissue t by the following equation adapted from (22)
